LunaKeyPairGeneratorEcWithExtraRandomBits
public class LunaKeyPairGeneratorEc
extends KeyPairGeneratorSpi

Engine class for generating EC DSA key pairs. By default this class will generate keys on the secp384r1 curve.

initialize

public void initialize(AlgorithmParameterSpec params,
                       SecureRandom random)
                throws InvalidAlgorithmParameterException
Initializes the key pair generator with the given parameter spec. The parameter spec must describe a supported named curve.

The Luna HSM supplies its own source of randomness so the random parameter is ignored.

Overrides:
initialize in class KeyPairGeneratorSpi
Parameters:
params - the parameter set used to generate the keys. Must be an object of class ECParameterSpec
random - unused
Throws:
InvalidAlgorithmParameterException - if the given parameters are inappropriate for this key pair generator.
